Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.79,0:00:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在你眼前  有著無限的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.35,0:00:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照亮了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海底兩萬哩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭懦弱的人  無法背叛藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在作夢之前  我想翱翔天際
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中的音樂盒開啟  發出聲響
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點一滴演奏出幸福與勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:01:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在你眼前  有著無限的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.44,0:01:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言語是永遠的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.77,0:01:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't  forget  to  try  in  mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.73,0:01:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛比寶石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.62,0:01:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.54,0:01:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時值西元1889年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.61,0:01:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了逃離企圖奪取\N"蔚藍之水"的邪惡三人組
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幸在海上漂流的強\N娜蒂亞與大王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.68,0:01:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到美國戰艦的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.11,0:01:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是戰艦卻在\N神秘大海獸的攻擊下重創
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.65,0:01:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強他們也被迫\N再度回到海上漂流
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.89,0:01:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#04  萬能潛水艇鸚鵡螺號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個孩子究竟是到哪去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.61,0:02:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,韓森\N我們要在這裡待到什麼時候?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等到晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.41,0:02:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上藉由星星就能曉得位置
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時再到最近的島嶼去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.18,0:02:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桑森
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.76,0:02:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算穿那身裝扮到什麼時候?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到我能洗澡的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下身為堂堂紳士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能因為炎熱就穿著邋遢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的原則
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.74,0:02:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就快去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.37,0:02:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了就煩!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.71,0:02:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我都遇不到好男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我的運氣會這麼差呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神來吧\N都不像妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:02:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是跟我在一起\N才害你有這種下場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.33,0:03:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在死前我要先向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.47,0:03:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一點都不介意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.30,0:03:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟妳在一起我覺得很快樂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強,我是在跟大王道歉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.68,0:03:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肚子餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上抓條大魚給你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,可是我不吃魚喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在對大王說話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.29,0:03:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.26,0:03:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那頭海獸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又折回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,牠是怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一動也不動的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞,娜蒂亞呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是金屬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙並不是海獸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由人類製造出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是潛水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼莫船長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩名遇難者已經收容完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來這就是海獸的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是潛水艇,潛水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潛水艇?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以自由潛入海裡的船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.23,0:05:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個大發明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.17,0:05:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊沉戰艦與你爸爸的船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.17,0:05:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會就是這艘船?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.57,0:05:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是排水口嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:05:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很開心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭完新型戰艦之後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.45,0:06:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又能搭到這麼棒的潛水艇耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太走運了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看,這並沒有打鉚釘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎麼焊接的呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.49,0:06:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長,右舷兩點鐘方向\N出現微弱磁氣反應
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那傢伙嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離太過遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是那艘戰艦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不曉得,總之先接近再說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解,引擎啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.99,0:06:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是引擎的聲音,要啟航了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.56,0:06:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩舷全速,路線變更027
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.46,0:06:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.47,0:07:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要去哪裡呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不曉得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.07,0:07:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這具引擎已經掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磁氣反應未出現改變
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相對速度目前約32節
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的石像鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在死區雖然讓你溜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,我的運氣似乎還很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼莫船長\N請問要如何處置遇難者?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副艦長,是妳開口說要救人的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-交由妳處理吧\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個孩子似乎滿堅強的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您明明是討厭所有的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強,這艘船為什麼要救我們?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們被困在海上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.86,0:07:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許他們也跟那3個人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.63,0:08:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是為了想拿到"蔚藍之水"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.26,0:08:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔚藍之水!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣多疑不好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總比隨便相信人好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有門把\N但這個應該是門沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要拜託這艘船上的人\N讓我參觀船艙內部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.49,0:08:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有人啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不會傷害你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.11,0:08:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧,娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船可能是那隻海中怪獸耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,連面都還沒見過\N說話這麼失禮不好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對別人客氣一點\N這樣對自己也比較好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位公主名叫娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我則是王子,名叫強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎,謝謝你,強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是艾麗朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.83,0:09:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞,他人的好意\N妳就接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞,走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.17,0:09:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以參觀船艙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且"蔚藍之水"沒有發光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就表示沒有危險,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好窄又好奇怪的走廊喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.15,0:09:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬梆梆又古怪的門
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問妳就是艾麗朵拉?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯,進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.17,0:09:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N你們先把濕衣服換下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.91,0:09:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確,這個房間好涼快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:10:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為房裡有冷氣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷氣?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對,夏天也能讓房間\N保持涼爽的發明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天還能這麼涼爽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是人類最大的享受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是怎樣的構造?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.83,0:10:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點之後再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們先去沖個澡\N換上乾淨的衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沖澡?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是熱可可亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,0:10:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好神奇的裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是魔法嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是,這是科學的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確\N這艘船根本就是科學的精華嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.76,0:10:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是哪個國家的船?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不像是法國
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那會是英國,還是美國?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不屬於任何一個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.37,0:10:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是海盜嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是追捕海盜的那一方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼要戴上那種面具?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要沒看過我們的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算回到陸地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒辦法告訴他人\N你們見過什麼人對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是一群已經和陸地\N斷絕關係的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以希望你們能將\N在這裡見過的事全都忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳願意讓我們回去嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.33,0:11:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,我們目前正在追蹤\N重要的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間放你們下船
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我一定會負起責任\N將你們送回陸地上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.18,0:11:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼莫船長也把你們交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼莫?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得"尼莫"在拉丁文裡\N代表著"什麼人都不是"的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.52,0:11:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,你懂得真多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那並不是他的本名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻是最適合船長的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.13,0:11:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那艾麗朵拉也不是妳的本名嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.33,0:11:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就任憑你們想像了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每天會送兩次餐點過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然少了點\N但就先忍忍囉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.05,0:12:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見,你們要好好相處喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這顆"蔚藍之水"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我被賣到馬戲團的時候\N就帶在身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說我身上就只有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候妳幾歲?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不曉得…那時候我還很小
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有"蔚藍之水"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能成為我尋找家人的線索
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熄燈了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是代表晚上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有窗戶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:13:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不曉得\N現在是白天還是晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連這艘船要去哪裡也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之,這應該是叫我們該睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.28,0:13:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強,你醒著嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.41,0:13:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是覺得這艘船不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是艾麗朵拉對我們很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會平白無故對別人好\N一定另有企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我…遇到的人都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,我想發明了\N這麼厲害潛水艇的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.97,0:13:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會是壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們或許是害了你爸爸的人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不一定是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要凡事都往不好的方面想啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要先請他們\N讓我參觀這艘船的機械設備
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再慢慢想以後的事就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:13:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:14:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並沒有討厭的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.16,0:14:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對,前半部停機庫的飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何?有辦法修嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把引擎換掉也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,沒錯\N就照你的意思改裝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.78,0:14:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請盡快,那就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是到這裡來之後吃的\N第5頓玉米湯、麵包及牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.63,0:14:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說已經3天了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要到什麼時候才能出去呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.93,0:14:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.47,0:14:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論按哪個鍵都打不開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被鎖住了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦?強
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之,我想請他們\N先讓我參觀船艙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:15:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們連臉都不肯讓你看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會讓你參觀船艙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風好涼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.98,0:15:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是艾麗朵拉說的冷氣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.82,0:15:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是燈光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長,請立刻前來艦橋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌握到了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是,艦首2點鐘方向\N發現引擎聲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-立刻進行測距\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到目標
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方位32度,距離9200
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是石像鬼的潛水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約8節,正朝本艦航行中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被發現了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主動聲納呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.04,0:16:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並未發出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.54,0:16:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要攻擊嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,先按兵不動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.04,0:16:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-以距離5千追蹤敵艦\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.82,0:16:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要找出\N石像鬼的基地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定就在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預定接觸位置還有300秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.39,0:16:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近至8800
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,在被對方聲納發現前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行無聲潛航
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:16:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦停止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.27,0:16:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行無聲潛航
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主引擎停止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.58,0:17:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船停下來了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.45,0:17:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水深固定於120
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輔助引擎停止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩舷平衡一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.12,0:17:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自動懸吊,切換完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度3節
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消磁裝置,開始運作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦啟動防爆魚雷防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.70,0:17:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦啟動防爆魚雷防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防水閘門封閉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有水密艙門固定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,固定結束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防爆準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.61,0:17:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熄燈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.65,0:17:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的情況如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是,距離7500
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方位及速度不變
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是推進器遭戰艦破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.12,0:17:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是陷阱?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.03,0:17:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離接近至7000
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離接近至5000
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離3000
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能發出聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.99,0:18:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是那兩個孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.11,0:18:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不曉得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度、方位皆不變
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.41,0:18:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未發出主動聲納,距離1200
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:18:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以肉眼確認目標
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將通過本艦上方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼聲音?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有東西正從上面經過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.22,0:19:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深水炸彈,從正上方過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎全開,垂直上升
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受損情況呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.56,0:20:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第1輔助引擎中彈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.82,0:20:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦首右舷中彈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進水極輕微
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.09,0:20:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從7時至7時5分方向\N逐漸遠離
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.93,0:20:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離800,速度12節
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓它跑了\N左舷迴轉160度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵測到魚雷發射聲\N4枚,距離1200
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全速迴避
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.39,0:20:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魚雷防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.41,0:20:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受損情形呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.75,0:21:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未遭擊中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.08,0:21:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並無進水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.48,0:21:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓載一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉回水平位置
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.82,0:21:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.85,0:21:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到,聲波混亂無法辨識
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.49,0:21:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航海儀器及電羅經也全部失常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.26,0:21:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船身周圍遭強力磁場覆蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.10,0:21:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魚雷之中似乎含有妨礙物質
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在移動會有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.27,0:21:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦停止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被擺了一道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又得重頭來過
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.51,0:22:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人都出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.15,0:22:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外頭,該說再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.35,0:22:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.02,0:22:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒見到太陽了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.19,0:22:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,我還是沒能參觀到船艙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.07,0:22:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒,變成水上飛機了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.70,0:22:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.64,0:22:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是鸚鵡螺號和我所送的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.34,0:22:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸚鵡螺號?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.78,0:22:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對,萬能潛水艇鸚鵡螺號
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.48,0:22:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡往南飛會有座大島
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.19,0:22:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有船開往法國
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.55,0:22:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還在飛機裡放了羅盤、地圖\N以及一點食物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.76,0:22:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.66,0:22:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.56,0:23:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼莫船長給的時間\N只剩下5分鐘了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.87,0:23:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,妳還在做什麼,快來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.25,0:23:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.45,0:23:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳的幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.45,0:23:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,保重了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.44,0:23:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.51,0:23:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(待續)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.42,0:24:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼應付心中的焦急才好?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.59,0:24:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要看不清遠方的夢想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.66,0:24:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喃喃自語  仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.10,0:24:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你的約定耀眼閃爍著
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.04,0:24:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try  安慰的話語\N是傳達不到內心的風
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.15,0:24:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然背負的不安逐漸膨脹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.90,0:24:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這是我自己的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.20,0:24:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人應該也不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.84,0:24:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使跌倒或感到迷惘\N仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.59,0:25:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開鸚鵡螺號
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.33,0:25:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,載著我們兩個人\N與一隻動物的飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.79,0:25:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然遭到攻擊而墜落
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.76,0:25:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本和平的島嶼\N遭到侵略者佔領
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.60,0:25:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化為一座恐怖之島
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.47,0:25:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞,這孩子還活著\N她還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.07,0:25:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉…振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.08,0:25:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海底兩萬哩  下一回\N「瑪莉之島」
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.88,0:25:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-要看喔\N-要看喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
